Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MY FATHER'S SALARY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? It started\Nto drink milk by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Lassie, you grow up quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What-- what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has teeth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie's teeth had appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Small... small, but real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you upset the puppies, it wouldn't be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Always serious, always going out since dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,John...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, it's breakfast time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My father joins\Nthe morning march of the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there were more nurses in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It eats well, it's already bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't eat too much, Lassie!\NLeave some food for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is my father's salary day,\Ntomorrow is my mother's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, but what if there's\Na surgery on my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps there is a patient in critical\Ncondition, and prevents me from returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always pray that people\Nof Greenor Bridge to be in good health!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Always pray for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the house, when I come\Nback I'll go to the store to buy dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's getting closer, take your places!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now push hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be glad,\Nbecause today is the payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I heard well? He said: Be glad...\Ntoday... is the payday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone worked hard, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is pay monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter, it's important\Nnot to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you think I made a mistake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do my best to keep my salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wants only Mr. Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I received news from the bottom that\Nthe water came out of the second channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to go down and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is no one at the bottom\Nwanting to get wet with water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eli!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go down while we're busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your companion, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for making you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that person's speaking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Carraclough is already appreciated here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the office work is shared by us,\Nhe left it to me and went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy! So glad! Today is our payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well let's get going!\NSandy, get up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have stepped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is beautiful today, grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, more beautiful than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The mine workers are working hard\Nto get their salary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today is the payday,\Nsurely everyone will buy delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who don't work will not eat anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but those who work hard\Nwill eat until they are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The village of Greenor Bridge\Nis straight ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes that's right, are you going to trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it over there?\NAre there many customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as it is usual, because people\Nreceived their salaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I understand... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certainly a large\Nnumber of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When the mine's payday comes,\Ntraders come from everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here Lassie! There are lots of stands here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many farmers\Nwho sell very tasty vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of food my mother will cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward for tonight, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have finally finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My energy is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When will you give it to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I must put the president's salary\Nin the treasury first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, and give me my salary immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Group II, Bio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bio... Bio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! 3 pounds and 10 shillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Group II, Hamilton!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamilton, Hamilton...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here it is, hurry up, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Group II, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of water is not great,\Nyou will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your salary right away\Nand buy good food for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to fix it before water increses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:08:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do? I don't think you\Nwill enjoy your holiday, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his daughter gave birth to his\Ngranddaughter and is coming here to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, you are a talkative man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, if so, I can take his place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm a new worker and I want\Nto learn how to stop the water leakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will also stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in fact I can only say that you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to finish it quickly,\NMelissa and John are waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks delicious, Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of watching the food,\NI have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up, kid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in silverware?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Let's go, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sandy's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah John, I've got it from Lake Dartford.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You got all of it from the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't it look delicious?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy's there, with my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,John! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello John, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you eat a free watermelon? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, only you and Lassie came?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my father haven't returned yet\Nso I went first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, Sandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is my mother's birthday,\Nwhat kind of gift do you think she wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Sandy! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In here! In here! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, choose the one for your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make your wife more beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good choice, as you expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So... jewelry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I have no money...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing wrong with buying\Nthe gift together with your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to wait for my father, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go to the office to get your salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eli!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He left before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough, salary is in the treasury...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have completed the delivery\Nof salaries to all employees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you received your salary yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet... does it take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! You don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is your salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you've done extra work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Well, see you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have forgotten\Nto put Brock's salary in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Eli is not accurate\Nin his calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no salary because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't celebrate my wife's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have his leg exactly like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost it! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost all your salary! But what will you do\Ntomorrow at my mother's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's why... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know where you lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go after receiving your salary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think about my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't do anything as long as we lose it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The bathroom is hot, go immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're all black!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are you so, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All the important things are overflowing\Nand distracting yourself with trivial things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will borrow this to restore it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was doing everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, I've done something really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to us when I said you lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You used this excuse to lie to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible, I didn't lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent your money helping people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bathroom is ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, he is our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he will act like children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, you're a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you pick my father's smell\Nand recover his money?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My father went somewhere, and lost his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, well done!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my father's job is on the hillside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's impossible for it to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam apparently returned home\Nafter climbing the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to trust Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was down the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my father come here\Nwhen he came back from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, it's twice the way home\Nand it's hard for you to determine the route.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Lassie, if you go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was completely satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is very busy, and this\Nis due to the delivery of salaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have increased my salary\Nand estimated my extra work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard and treating\Npeople well is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to tell you!\NSee you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling good, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that? It seems I've seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a miner anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my father having fun when he came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People began to dissipate again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that he lost the money\Nbefore coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if the money fell here,\Nit will be hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did my father come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, keep it away, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hey, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the dog quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a game for the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago a man came from the mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,covered in coal and touched the brooch\Nand wanted to sell it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the person covered\Nwith coal looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a skinny man, who seems\Nto have stepped out of his job recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to get this brooch\Nand said he'll pay me the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to give\Nan expensive gift to a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said to him, "Stop this, this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer angry with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I think my father like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thief!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him! He just stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a thief!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's there! Catch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow him! Maybe he stole\Nmy father's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This crook guy stole my wallet too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I really apologize, Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell to the manager\Nto open the closet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like I'm about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only óne to blame and\Nthe victim is you, Mr. Caraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, let's talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See you on Monday, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected, you've done a good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a shy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, just a moment... come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh!\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't find the money, but look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you wanted to give\Nthis gift to my mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be eating your birthday tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay not to worry about the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will look forward to tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stupid village!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was robbed, and rewarded that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He have chosen that excellent brooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't go back to this village again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today is Saturday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a holiday for everyone,\Nbut not for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now Lassie, let's go to the lake today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to catch something to cook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\N6 MILES IN SEARCH FOR FOOD{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
